The '''Galactic Polysapient Medical Center''', also known as '''Big Zoo''', was a multi-sentient-species [[Medcenter/Legends|medcenter]] located on [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]], which not only treated [[Carbon/Legends|carbon]]-based beings, but also had facilities for treating halogen and [[Silicon/Legends|silicon]]-based life forms as well. It was home to 73 different environs and corresponding operating rooms.

